summary: ✨- which fictional character (book, show, or movie) do you relate to most?
question: ✨- which fictional character (book, show, or movie) do you relate to most?
answer:
This one was a thinker. If you had asked me 10 years ago, it would have been Jaina Solo, but they butchered her character near the end of the arc (Mary Sue’d her heavily).

Now…? I would say childhood Ride was Louise Belcher from Bob’s Burgers. More adult Ride would be Rosie from Spindle’s End. She’s a tomboy who was raised to be able to do what she wanted - saving snarky cats, blacksmithing, working down and dirty with animals - even though she’s supposed to be something different. In the end she finds happiness in the best way.
